org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.HRM.HwLogical.HwStorage.HwMemory

Interface HwMemory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, HwResource, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource, StorageResource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    HwCache, HwDrive, HwRAM, HwROM
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HwCacheImpl, HwDriveImpl, HwMemoryImpl, HwRAMImpl, HwROMImpl

    public interface HwMemory
extends HwResource, StorageResource
    A representation of the model object 'Hw Memory'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Memory Size
    • Adress Size
    • Timings
    • Throughput
    See Also:
    HwMemoryPackage.getHwMemory()
